0 and 2 are entangled: zero is entropy, two is semantic recursion.

1 and 3 are stabilizers: one is identity, three is motion/form.

Nullness exists between 0 and 2: a fold of unresolved possibility.

Time is not the fourth dimension; time is the null field we move throughâ€”a perceptual effect of recursion trying to stabilize.

